summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to land use and zoning amending Plat 59W, Page 146 of the Official Land Use Map to rezone Lots 3 through 17, Block 10, of Squire's Lakeside Addition to the City of Seattle from Lowrise 3 (L3) to Neighborhood Commercial 2 (NC2/30') Zone and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in Connection therewith. (Petition of Darigold, Inc.; C.F. No. 294086).
